#

French-Style Pork Tenderloin with Savory Herb Gravy

$25.99
550 kcal

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freehigh-proteinlow-carb

Tags:

FrenchPorkGourmetHerb Infusion

Description

A succulent pork tenderloin braised to perfection, complemented by a fragrant herb-infused gravy, ideal for a gourmet dining experience.

Ingredients

  • Pork tenderloin: 1.5 lbs
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Shallots: 2, chopped
  • Fresh thyme: 2 sprigs
  • Fresh rosemary: 2 sprigs
  • Chicken broth: 1 cup
  • Heavy cream: 1/2 cup
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
